{"tid":284181,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"AV女優相約出遊迪士尼　日本鄉民痛罵不要臉","createTime":"2017-06-14T16:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T13:11:39.000Z","uid":10338,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f89be61a7575e6da5d63315fac662fcb8cb5498","tid":284181,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:58:36.000Z","msg":"AV女優吉澤明步日前在自己的推特上貼了一張一群女生集體出遊迪士尼的照片，照片中除了她自己之外，還有葵司、麻美由真、西野翔等AV女優。沒想到這張照片被日本鄉民轉貼到了《2CH》，底下800多則留言幾乎一面倒的批評她們「不要臉」，憑什麼來「夢之國」丟人現眼？<br />\n「該不會是來拍AV的吧」、「好醜」、「妳們應該去雞雞展示館玩啊」，還有鄉民指稱她們沒有假裝普通女孩的權利，「難道沒有一點身為垃圾的自覺嗎？」<br />\n小小一張照片，讓人看出了日本這個社會性開放的同時，卻又極度壓抑的矛盾特性。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"3a9b18c8fa9002209b99584d89a6cac38f36d6b9","tid":284181,"uid":833,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:59:55.000Z","msg":"留言者係女性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33139a5d1c08ece0c93d01884e62dac1363959e7","tid":284181,"uid":10338,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T17:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留言者係女性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tomcat.2ch.sc/test/read.cgi/livejupiter/1497155128/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftomcat.2ch.sc%2Ftest%2Fread.cgi%2Flivejupiter%2F1497155128%2F&d=6aziMsnRwHdMoDGbW9FKtf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=bc509ef2\" target=\"_blank\">http://tomcat.2ch.sc/test/read.cgi/livejupiter/1497155128/</a><br />\n唔識日文 但見佢地用晒咩悲報 売春婦 園内で撮影<br />\n穢れた人間  歩く性病<br />\n係幾惡毒下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3ad97ff632f58da46e0b2f5ec83c0255fca938","tid":284181,"uid":83531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T17:24:59.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0136497e23b45efd4323162b48248b8ffbc6fef5","tid":284181,"uid":117868,"